  <brief_title>Tumor and Treatments Impact on Neurocognitive Functions and Quality of Life of Patients With OMS Grade II Glioma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tumor and Treatments Impact on Neurocognitive Functions and Quality of Life of Patients With OMS Grade II Glioma: Multicentric Prospective Study</official_title>
