  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter prospective study:2 independant cohorts of patients with OMS grade II
      glioma will be followed during 5 years.

        -  cohort A: patients in first-line treatment (surgery, radiotherapy or chemotherapy)

        -  cohort B: patients with disease simple monitoring.

      The primary endpoint is to evaluate the impact of tumor and treatments on neurocognitive
      functions and quality of life, using validate and standard tests.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
