  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  OMS grade II glioma

          -  signed informed consent

          -  age &gt;=18

          -  IK &gt;=80%

          -  ability to read, write and undertand French

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  glioma localized to brainstem

          -  other neurologic or psychiatric disease

          -  history of other malignancies, other than curatively treated in-situ carcinoma of the
             cervix or basal cell carcinoma of the skin, or any other curatively treated cancer
             with no sign of recurrence within 5 years prior to randomization

          -  neuroleptic concomitant treatment

          -  pregnant or lactating women
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
